public class ArtistDao
extends SimpleRDF4JCRUDDao<Artist,​IRI>
    Class responsible for repository access for managing Artist entities. The class extends the SimpleRDF4JCRUDDao, providing capabilities for inserting and reading entities.

    4.0.0
